snippet.title: Last Day Lockdown - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Bid farewell to the mundane and embrace the extraordinary as you step into "Last Day Lockdown," a thrilling office escape puzzle that transforms your farewell into an unforgettable journey!

Beta will be released at Gamescom Asia 2023
